Changelog from 6/5/97 to 6/16/97:
 - Added operand combination to VergeC. (All old VCs will need to be recompiled)
 - Took a 4 day vacation to kentucky.
 - Got revamped maps from Hahn. (Probably the "major" deal of this version)
 - Fixed up a stupid control bug in the Status Screen making the left arrow
   work as if it were the right arrow.
 - Added a GP window to the main menu.
 - Fixed up the Banner command to keep the tile animations going while it's
   in control.
